Source: deng-iwad-doom2-installer
Section: universe/games
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Jamie Jones <jamie_jones_au@yahoo.com.au>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0)
Standards-Version: 3.6.2

Package: deng-iwad-doom2-installer
Architecture: all
Depends: deng, glbsp
Description: deng installer for doom2.wad
 This will install your doom2.wad file for use with The Doomsday Engine,
 and other Doom engines.
 .
 You will be prompted for the location of your doom2.wad file so it
 can be copied to the correct location for IWADS.
 .
 It will also run GLBSP on your IWAD to create a .gwa file for Doom engines
 such as The Doomsday Engine and EDGE that need them.
 
